analysis.description: The kitchen features a modern Indian design with a minimalist approach. The use of purple cabinetry and white marble backsplash creates a contemporary yet elegant look. The black refrigerator and kitchen island add a modern touch, while the open-plan layout enhances the space's functionality. No traditional Indian elements are present, focusing on a sleek and contemporary aesthetic.

metadata.budget_indicator: High, due to use of high-end materials like marble and purple cabinetry
metadata.functionality: Primary purpose is for cooking and preparing meals, with an open-plan layout for social interaction
